Diamond - Rabbit
Rabbit - 6th of 10 art from the "Diamond Animals" collection.
Belief in the magical properties of the rabbit's foot is widespread in many places around the world, including Europe, China, Africa, North and South America. In the era of digital art, you can add a lucky diamond bunny to your collection.
